178
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:26,100
- I'm all right. <br> - Chen Minjue!

179
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:27,198
You!

180
00:10:27,199 --> 00:10:29,140
If you ever bully my sister again,

181
00:10:29,140 --> 00:10:31,220
