195
00:10:59,160 --> 00:11:01,460
- Little Six. <br> - Yes?

196
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:04,514
- Whose side are you on? <br> - I...

197
00:11:04,514 --> 00:11:08,199
Linglong, did you forget why Aunt Yinghong asked us to come here?

198
