209
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:35,239
We can go check out if there're any handsome men first.

210
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,300
Let's go.

211
00:11:36,300 --> 00:11:38,719
You're acting improperly

212
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,780
